summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 20150, entitled "An Ordinance authorizing the City Engineer, under certain conditions, to complete a certain portion of the improvement of Eighteenth Avenue and Eighteenth Avenue North, et al, in the City of Seattle, and appropriating money therefor, and under certain conditions declaring certain contractors and certain surety companies to be in default, and barred from city business for a period of time," approved February 9, 1909.
